cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision and image analysis techniques for recognizing materials inside transparent containers. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the automation of laboratory processes, which suggests that it may belong to cs.RO (Robotics and Automation). The use of machine learning and image analysis techniques for material recognition suggests that it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) as it deals with image analysis and recognition.
